packages.name: MobileAnalyzer
packages.author: RoundedRectangle
packages.long_description:
Reads protected system files

To use:
1. In the stweak ettings, enter the path you would like to read
2. Apply the tweak
3. Go to Settings app -> Privacy & Security > Analytics & Improvements > Analytics Data
4. Select `RoundedAnalytics-file.txt`, where `file` is your file name
